{"tid":1596681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最新風向:叫人唔好去對話，成立獨立調查委員會就收貨","createTime":"2019-09-26T15:08:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T15:23:12.000Z","uid":100337,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b9c73a47dcf581e15bd31f62a803c84a86638761","tid":1596681,"uid":100337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T15:08:05.000Z","msg":"點解唔好去對話?有得喺電視機前當面屌柒777同重申五大訴求，決一不可，唔係最好嘅文宣咩？<br />\n成立獨立調查委員會場運動就散?我諗好多人驚淺黃會收貨，咁呢個時候就要靠文宣，話俾佢地聽冇一個民主嘅政府，係唔會有一個公正嘅獨立調查。<br />\n攞沙中線中科最近嘅聲明就係最好文宣。<br />\n<br />\n雖然曙光唔知幾時會見到，但一日未見到，一日都唔可以放棄。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">願榮光歸香港</span></span>"},{"pid":"d39ef073471f62202db26252e06225cd08dabb3c","tid":1596681,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T15:09:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6563d305234478bdcfdfbd5f9ac8812f89b1a79b","tid":1596681,"uid":100337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T15:11:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d233c0f44d31f6882fb799cf54e93442047952d2","tid":1596681,"uid":100337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T15:23:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}